import { StyleSheet } from "@react-pdf/renderer"

import global from "./global"

export default StyleSheet.create({
  ...global,

  container: {
    border: "1px solid black",
    position: "absolute",
    right: "50%",
    display: "flex",
    flexDirection: "row-rewerse",
    margin: "20 10",
    padding: "20 10",
    padingTop: 5,
    width: "49%",
    height: "100%",
  },
})
